<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ginna tha a lengin, kalvari tang lamah va chieh leng,
 Ka Lalpa thihna mun achun;
 Ka chenna ding Salem thak va mung ie.

[V2]
 Ka lei lungkham kah sawlang bang tang ie,
 Nawpna pak lunna gam nuom thil leng.

[V3]
 2. Kalvari tang chunga thisan lui luong Hukdampa nak ah,
 Namtin silthienna mun achun;
 Aw ka thagau, ziechun va buol in.

[V4]
 3. Jerusalem thak khu a kilatna tang dang a um puoi,
 Thil hitiu Kalvari tang ah;
 Ziechun a lang Hukdampa nak achun.

[V5]
 4. Aw ka thagau leng in na Hukdampa thihna mun achun,
 Nangmah zieka a thawkna chu;
 A thisan luong ah va kisil in.</lyrics>
<title>Ginna Tha A Leng In</title>
<hymn_number>53</hymn_number>
<author>Lianvela</author>
</song>